### Business Context
- **Founder**: Tiago Martins (solo employee)
- **Focus**: Consumer infrastructure that makes better living effortless
- **Portfolio**: 16 brands across creation, investment, and advisory
- **Contact**: hey@notacompany.com

## Tech Stack

- **Framework**: Next.js 15 (App Router, Static Generation)
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **Styling**: Minimal CSS (classic HTML aesthetic)
- **Fonts**: Times New Roman (serif)
- **Analytics**: Seline + Vercel Speed Insights
- **Deployment**: Vercel

## Pages

- `app/page.tsx`: Homepage with about section
- `app/portfolio/page.tsx`: Portfolio listing with filters
- `app/portfolio/[slug]/page.tsx`: Individual brand pages (16 total)

## Development Guidelines

### Code Quality
```bash
pnpm run fix-all       # Auto-fix everything  
pnpm run check-all     # Verify all passes
```

### Code Style
- TypeScript with strict settings
- Server Components preferred
- Minimal dependencies
- Simple, readable code

### Content Guidelines
- First person ("I" not "we")
- Human, approachable tone
- No corporate speak or buzzwords
- Keep it simple and honest

## Key Files

- `app/globals.css`: Classic HTML styling (Times, blue links, hr)
- `lib/brands.ts`: Brand data utilities
- `content/brands/`: 16 MDX files with brand info
- `public/llms.txt`: LLM context file
- `public/favicons/`: Favicon assets

## Important Notes

- **No OG meta tags** - keeping it minimal
- **No fancy UI components** - pure HTML aesthetic
- **Static generation** for all pages
- Footer credits: world's first website + GitHub links

